text: Infopark or InfoPark may refer to one of the following IT-focused business parks in Kerala, India: * InfoPark, Kochi, located in the Kakkanad region of Kochi, Ernakulam district * InfoPark Thrissur, in Koratty, Thrissur district * Infopark Cherthala, in Cherthala, Alappuzha district
title: Infopark
